title.narrative: Communications and media activities effectively promote child rights.

description.narrative: The media and external relations section worked to promote the cause of children in Madagascar by conducting vigorous outreach on the challenges and achievements in the realisation of their rights. This was done through media relations, digital content creation, social media growth, partnerships events and trainings. The main audiences of this outreach were: the donor community (both established and targeted); domestic and international media; digital and non-digital influencers, and the engaged global public. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
